# Supported Platforms

* CentOS 7
* Ubuntu 14.04
* FreeBSD 10

# Parameters

* conf:
    group(string): Group for users that may execute commands as root via sudo
    group_nopw(string): Like group, but without password
    policies(list):
      name(string): Username or group the policy applies to
      nopasswd(bool, False): Do not require a password
      targets(list of string): Allowed commands
